IN RE the MARRIAGE OF Elizabeth M. WILSON and Gabriel W. Wilson Upon the Petition of Elizabeth M. Wilson, Petitioner-Appellee, And Concerning Gabriel W. Wilson, Respondent-Appellant. No. 17-1302 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed February 6, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

A husband appeals the decree dissolving his marriage. AFFIRMED AS MODIFIED.

AFFIRMED AS MODIFIED.
